snippet.title: Married at First Sight: What happened to Dave and Amber After the Show?
snippet.description:
Dave and Amber were a popular couple on Married at First Sight Season 7. They might have said yes on the Decision Day but said no to holding on to it forever, as they parted their ways shorty later. Everyone who joins the show doesn’t return home with a partner, and that’s what happened with Dave and Amber. They may not have found their soul mate in the reality show but indeed found themselves.
